front.title: Quick Reflexes
front.gametext: Deploy on your side of table. During your draw phase, you make use 2 Force to search through your Lost Pile. Take one Hidden Weapons into hand or take any one blaster and immediately deploy it (for free).
front.lore: Boba Fett's helmet has infrared capabilities, a motion tracking system, a macrobinocular viewer, an internal comlink and a broadband antenna. He doesn't miss a thing.

pulls: Any one blaster from Lost Pile
